      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle with plenty of life left? This car is in fair condition and ready to hit the road! It\u2019s been a reliable companion and, while it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for a functional ride at a great value. With a little bit of TLC, this car will continue to serve you well for years to come!",
