    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature high-revving redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a suspension refresh featuring Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings to maintain optimal camber under load. Mechanically robust, this unit has undergone proactive VANOS servicing and a rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for long-term structural integrity. While showing honest cosmetic wear consistent with an enthusiast's weekend car, the powertrain and steering rack remain exceptionally communicative and sharp.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
